SVTnIR300W

  Recall queued for Virtual( ) Physical( ) has not started. Make sure a
  RecallServer is active

  Reason:
  A recall has remained unassigned by a RecallServer beyond the dynamic options
  RecallServerTimeout value. The recall remains queued.

  Action:
  Start a subsystem customized as RecallServer=Server or dynamically change an
  existing subsystem to handle the recall.
